               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="15r">1v-15r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s27IHA">قران, Twentieth ǧuz’ (20/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#2r">-2r</locus>فَمَا كَانَ جَوَابَ قَوْمِهِ إِلَّا أَنْ قَالْوْا اَخْرِجُوْا اَلَ لُوْطٍ مِنْ قَرْيَتِكُم اِنَهُمْ (sic) اُنَاسٌ يَتَطِّهَرُوْنَ  <note>v. 56 is the beginning of the ḥizb; ǧuz’ 20 starts v. 60.</note>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#15r">-15r</locus>وَلَذِكْرُ اللهِ أَكْبَرُ وَاللهُ يَعْلَمُ مَا تَصْنَعُوْنَ<note>v. 45 is the end of the ḥizb; ǧuz’ 20 ends v. 44.</note>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>27:56-29:44. Irregular ihmāl signs (rā’s, sīns, ‘ayns). Different hand f. 12r, last 4 lines. 12 lines a page. Rubricated title of suras. Noticable execution of some lām-lā (ex. 4v, 5r, 9v, 10v). Words completed the following line in many places from the beginning to the end of the ǧuz’. Few words, which were started on a line, were entirely rewritten the following line. (6r, 9v). Catchwords added lately. Deletions, and corrections after revision.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
